Here's a PlantUML component diagram for the CodisLabs_codis repository, focusing on deployment architecture:

@startuml CodisLabs_codis

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor LightSkyBlue
  BorderColor Black
}

[Client Applications] as Client

package "Codis Cluster" {
  [Codis Proxy] as Proxy
  [Codis Dashboard] as Dashboard
  [Codis FE] as FE
  database "ZooKeeper/Etcd" as ZK
}

package "Redis Servers" {
  [Redis Server 1] as Redis1
  [Redis Server 2] as Redis2
  [Redis Server N] as RedisN
}

Client --> Proxy : Requests
Proxy --> Redis1
Proxy --> Redis2
Proxy --> RedisN
Proxy <--> Dashboard : Monitoring & Management
Dashboard <--> ZK : Cluster Metadata
FE <--> Dashboard : Admin UI
FE <--> ZK : Read Cluster Info

note right of Proxy
  Load balancing &
  Transparent sharding
end note

note right of Dashboard
  Cluster management &
  Monitoring
end note

note right of ZK
  Cluster configuration &
  Coordination
end note

@enduml